{"word":"διαδύνω","slug":"διαδύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαδύνω</b></el> <el>(or <el>-δύω</el>) (more commonly as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>διαδύομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δύσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>διέδυν</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to slip through</i> a hole or gap, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to slip through, slip away</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to evade, shirk</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}